ana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">What you get when you hit 55</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Wuz with other wizzies we all 54-55 last night and were lamenting that unlike other classes (e.g. Mages who get CoH), 55 holds nothing special for us (in fact the whole 52-58 range is pretty disappointing in terms of power upgrades).<br>
