E'ci <I>Lords of Light</I><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugrimstafftheurgist.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Grimstaff Theurgist</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www,kestrelarts.com/images/book.jpg BORDER=0></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Sorcerer</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>4/26/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>11:12:25 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: What you get when you hit 55</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Yeah but at 50 we got Translocate, and nobody else gets anything that great then.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#33333><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udarret.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Darret</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Apprentice</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>4/26/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>11:31:16 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: What you get when you hit 55</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Whats so great about Translocate??? Sure its great for classes that cant cast gate but how does tranlocate make wizards more likely to get a group, seems to me the majority of the times I use it is when I'm LFG at the zone.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ugherad.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Gherad</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Wizard</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>4/26/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>12:03:59 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: What you get when you hit 55</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Yeah, 52 to 60 is a long stretch in which we really get nothing new.  We have no new spell lines and only get different flavors of spells we already have.  I guess the only really big spell in that whole range is evacuate at level 57.<br>
<br>
Oh, and I think my most used spell from 55 is probably improved invis.  I just wish it was not self only.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#33333><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ucenelrontanknpuller.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Cenelron TankNPuller</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Apprentice</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>4/30/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>6:37:56 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: What you get when you hit 55</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">?!?!?!?!?   Are you insane?  Lvl 55 is one of the few levels where you do get significat spells in the 50s.<br>
<br>
IMPROVED INVISIBILITY!    If you do not see the HUGE advantage to this spell then I must wonder what game you are playing.<br>
<br>
Beyond that you get the following:<br>
<br>
Tears of Solusek to replace Tears of Druzzil.  Much more powerful being fire based rather than magic based, in addition to the greater base damage.<br>
<br>
Draught of Jiva.  Hmmm, and interrupt spell you can get off approximately every 3.5 seconds (with staff of flux or other instant cast item)?  How could this possibly be usefull?  In addition to the obvious usefullness against caster mobs or players, it interrupts without actually stunning mobs so unstunnable casters, such as giant Adjudants in Kael, can be interrupted.<br>
<br>
Lure of Flame.  You finally have a fire based lure worth using.<br>
<br>
<br>
If the only spell we got at 55 was Improved Invisibility then it would be a great level.  Granted it would be even nicer if we could cast it on others, but I'll settle for it saving MY skin.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> </font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#000000><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ufilanfyretracker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Filan Fyretracker</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif BORDER=0></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Forum Wizard</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>4/30/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>10:19:20 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Community Supporter</FONT><BR><BR><img src=http://pages.cthome.net/filanwizard/pic01.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: What you get when you hit 55</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">i rarely use rains anymore since 90% of the time i do use them druzz and solusk minimum of 1 wave is resisted but usualy 2</font><P><center><img src=http://pages.cthome.net/filanwizard/fizeau12.jpg><b><font color="#3333FF"><font size=+2><a href="mailto:filan@snet.net">Filan
